name: LIMITED EDITION "YOU WILL NOT SLEEP" T SHIRT
description:
Scott is an artist and hardcore singer with the band special move from essex, Ive been a big fan of his work for a long time and have managed to persuade him to let me screen print 20 limited edit...ion tee shirts of one of my favourite of his drawings called "you will not sleep".

I have been screen printing for a couple of years now, mainly doing my own designs, band merch and clothing for friends companys. It is something I love to do especially when I get to print artwork like this , Its a lot of work but seeing the finished result its well worth it.

Each T shirt is lovingly hand printed by moi on top quality gildan t shirts with a waterbased ink (which means it wont crack and age and go nasty like most t shirts).

We are going to print 20 and 20 only , this t shirt will never be printed ever again!!!!! so if you want to be one of only 20 people in the hole wide world with one of these then I suggest you email me or scott as soon as and make an order as these will go like hot cakes!!! I wore one the other day and everyone that saw it wanted one.

The price of this exclusivity and to be the proud owner of one of these shirts is a mere Â£25!!

 let me know what size you want when you order

name: "UGG ROAD RAT SHIRT" by David Dixon
description: This shirt is a hand printed reproduction of an original artwork by artist , skateboarder, film maker and creator of the harmony skateboard company David Dixon. In this artwork David pays homage to the artist ratfink who has had a massive influence on skateboard graphics and tattoo design in David's own unique and instantly recognisable style.
